Package: geographiclib
Title: Access to 'GeographicLib' 
Version: 0.3.7
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Sumner", , "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("cre")), 
    person("Charles", "Karney", role = c("cph", "aut"), comment="GeographicLib author and maintainer")
    )
Description: GeographicLib functions for precise geodetic calculations including 
    MGRS (Military Grid Reference System), UTM/UPS projections, Geohash encoding, 
    geodesic computations (distance, bearing, paths), and polygon area on the 
    WGS84 ellipsoid. All functions are fully vectorized with rich metadata output. 
SystemRequirements: C++17
